<p>AD had a session with a Bixby who was a thirteen-year old furry, and the whole town was his sex toys. My character was an anthropomorphic panda. When we found the bender, I ordered the shot, then while he was in shock I cold cocked him. Good thing when he died we didn't stay furries, but I figured better that than the end of &quot;I Have No Mouth And I Must Scream&quot;, y'know?</p>
<p>Personally, I wondered how he could be fellated by a hominid platypus, but I try not to get lost on the details.</p>

